title: Redwall
description: Seventh Trilling Redwall Adventure Redwall Abbey, Tranquil Home To A Community Of Peace-Loving Mice Is Threatened By Cluny The Scourge - The Evil-One-Eyed Rat Warlord -And His Battle-Hardened Horde Of Predators. Cluny Is Certain That Redwall Will Fall Easily To His Fearsome Army - But He Hasn'T Bargained For The Courage And Strength Of The Combined Forces Of The Redwall Mice, Their Loyal Woodland Friends. . . . .
